Finance-TickerSymbols version 0.01
==================================

SYNOPSIS

use Finance::TickerSymbols  ;

for my $symbol ( symbols_list( 'nasdaq' ) ) {

    # do something with $symbol
    # for example:
#    use Finance::YahooQuote ;
#    my @Q = getonequote $symbol ;
#    print "$Q[1] ($Q[0]) is $Q[2]\n" ;
}

NOTE: currently (version 0.01) only supports 'nasdaq', 'amex', and 'nyse' 


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::Simple

  (Installing CPAN's LWP bundle might be a good idea, one
  way of installing it is:
   % perl -MCPAN -e 'install Bundle::LWP'
   )
  

